snippet.title: Unblock Gem: Become a Jeweler
snippet.description:
Do you like puzzles? To think quietly, slowly , to take a break from the bustle of the day, to escape or kill time? How about to try yourself as a jeweler?
Try our game. Excellent for killing time and developing logical thinking.

Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wooloofun.unblockgem
AppStore - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/unblock-gem/id1200251714?mt=8

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/unblockgem
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WOOLooFunGames

Music from http://www.freesfx.co.uk
